<section id="fs-idp75946800" class="exercises"><title>Chemistry End of Chapter Exercises</title><exercise id="fs-idp18527664">
<problem id="fs-idm31250240">
<para id="fs-idp75695024">Which bond in each of the following pairs of bonds is the strongest?</para>
<para id="fs-idp174181168">(a) C–C or <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>C</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp191457408">(b) C–N or <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mo>≡</m:mo><m:mtext>N</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idm37995600">(c)<m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mo>≡</m:mo><m:mtext>O</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math> or <m:math><m:mrow><m:mtext>C</m:mtext><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mtext>O</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:math></para>
<para id="fs-idp19512320">(d) H–F or H–Cl</para>
